MonetDB PHP API documentation manual
------------------------------------

To generate manual for MonetDB PHP API you need to perform the following
steps:

- obtain phpdoc framework
  cvs -d :pserver:cvsread@cvs.php.net:/repository co phpdoc

- In the phpdoc directory make these modifications:

- modify RFC/manual.xml.in by adding
  &reference.monetdb.reference;
in group 
  refs.database.vendors

- modify entities/global.ent by adding
  <!ENTITY url.monetdb "http://monetdb.cwi.nl/">
  <!ENTITY url.monetdb.docs "http://monetdb.cwi.nl/TechDocs/">

- if you want to generate only MonetDB pages (full phpdoc generation
  takes quite some time) try to do this:
rm -rf en/reference/[a-z]*

- add MonetDB documentation from MonetDB distribution e.g. by running:
ln -s $MONETDB_SOURCE/src/mapi/clients/php/phpdoc/monetdb/ en/reference/monetdb

- clean possible old files
make clean
rm -rf autom4te.cache

- run generation scripts
autoconf
./configure
make

- the manual should be generated in 
  html/ref.monetdb.html

- to copy all MonetDB-specific pages to some directory just run
  cp *monetdb* <some_directory>
